data.description: This meticulously maintained single-owner residence offers 1,992 square feet of finished living space. The main level boasts an primary suite with a spacious walk-in closet and a private bath area, along with a versatile second bedroom currently utilized as an office. Downstairs in the finished walk-out lower level, you'll discover a comfortable third bedroom and an abundance of storage space, a cozy family room and an additional full bath. Enjoy outdoor living with a deck on the main level and a patio in the lower level. Plus, benefit from low monthly association dues and the opportunity for a swift possession. Reach out to schedule a private tour today.  All information obtained from Seller and public records.
